d a Bachelor of Science in biology from St. Joseph’s University and a Masters of Business Administration from Villanova University. LI profile: <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/michael-kamdar-085a7aa/" target="_blank">https://www.linkedin.com/in/michael-kamdar-085a7aa/</a>
