                                <b>Dr. Ken Kyoung Hoon Suh, CEO and Founder</b> Dr. Ken Kyoung Hoon Suh is the CEO and founder of E&S Healthcare, a commercial stage in vitro diagnostic company developing new and invaluable diagnostics from searching of novel or re-orienting protein biomarekrs from body fludis. Ken is a professor of Department of Biotechnology and Science, Pai Chai University since 1995. He has successfully completed a long-term government supporting project that formed a research cluster with industry, academia, and hospitals to discover biomarkers. Ken have been involved in many central and local governments’ planning and evaluation committees of bio-industry for over a decade. Ken earned a BS and a MS in biochemistry from Yonsei University. He had studied for a Ph.D. at Department of Phhysiology and Bioiphysics, University of Illinois at Chicago and worked at Department of Physiology and Pharmacology, University of Chicago as a post-doc and a research associate. He is serving as one of vice presidents of Bio-Healthcare Association that facilitates fruitful cooperation among all kinds of stakeholders in bio-economy.
